summary: Twenty-something Ana, now living in Buenos Aires, returns to her native city of Paraná. She meets old school mates, old friends, makes new ones, and starts to rethink her life, and perhaps change her future.
cast: Camila Toker|Ignacio Uslenghi|Juan Cruz Díaz la Barba|Natacha Massera|Analía Juan
title: Ana y los otros
